Articles.Content:
KSP x64 can have trouble writing to the settings.cfg depending on your system language, try deleting your settings.cfg, running KSP with "LC\_ALL=C ./KSP.x86\_64" and setting the graphics again.

You will need to use LC\_ALL every time, this is easier with a script like this.

    #!/bin/bashcd "/home/useraccountnamehere/.local/share/Steam/SteamApps/common/Kerbal Space Program/"LC_ALL=C ./KSP.x86_64
